Debian packaging for pkg-mediterranean-gtk-themes
-------------------------------------------------

A quick summary of how one can update the Debian packaging of
pkg-mediterranean-gtk-themes is to, assuming that one already has the
packages `devscripts`, `git-buildpackage`, and `pristine-tar` installed:

    gbp-clone --all git://github.com/rbrito/pkg-mediterranean-gtk-themes.git
    cd pkg-mediterranean-gtk-themes
    git checkout -- debian
    [ Make here some adaptations, like updating debian/changelog, if needed ]
    git-buildpackage

These are the important steps and may need to be changed according to
deviations, say, in the release process of pkg-mediterranean-gtk-themes.

